<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>7161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很久以前，路易斯安那州住着一个富有的地主。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的名字叫查尔斯·帝朗司。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22973</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他有两个快要结婚的女儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22974</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个女儿的婚礼将同一天于爸爸的农场举行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33608</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>帝朗司先生很爱他的女儿们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，他决定给她们一个巨大的惊喜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“婚礼就要举行了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48592</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有没有办法让那天变得更特别呢？”他心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51029</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在考虑了几天之后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想到了一个极好的主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他去跟他的仆人商量。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61682</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要很多的蜘蛛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61683</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我能从哪里找到呢？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在中国应该可以找到。”其中一位仆人回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您需要多少只蜘蛛？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要几百万只蜘蛛。”帝朗司说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仆人们很惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蜘蛛很贵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可能需要用船载到这里。”一位仆人解释道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>查尔斯还是预定了那些蜘蛛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个月以后，一整船的蜘蛛从中国运了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们拿这些蜘蛛做什么呢？”仆人问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把它们放在通往房子的路两旁的树上。”他指示说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123907</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么要放了这些蜘蛛？”仆人们不解。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123908</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132007</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“马上要到他女儿结婚的日子了。”他们很困惑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来的几天里，蜘蛛在树上结了很多网。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>帝朗司先生叫来他的仆人们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要你们到城里去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从加利福尼亚预定金粉和银粉各200公斤。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他刚才是叫我们去预定金粉和银粉各200公斤吗？”他们互相问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是这么说的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他当然有钱来买这些粉，但是他为什么需要这个呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仆人们很困惑，也很好奇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几天以后，金粉和银粉到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184474</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>查尔斯·帝朗司非常满意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天就是女儿结婚的日子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把粉末撒到蜘蛛网上！”他吩咐道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>帝朗司的指示再一次让仆人感到很惊讶，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200022</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他们还是按照他说的，把粉末撒到了蜘蛛网上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当一切完成之后，仆人们终于明白了帝朗司的计划。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>路边的蜘蛛网在阳光下闪闪发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快看啊！”宾客们很惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊，真是太美了！”他们惊叹道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238280</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美丽的，闪闪发光的蜘蛛网让每个来参加婚礼的人都惊讶无比。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238281</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246965</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是不是为你们策划了一场美丽的婚礼？”帝朗司对女儿们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246966</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸，太感谢你了！真是太美了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们高兴地回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。”她们的爸爸解释说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望你们能够拥有世界上最昂贵的婚礼！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>